{"tid":625361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰航空飛布里斯班客機　起飛4小時後折返","createTime":"2018-04-11T11:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T15:26:20.000Z","uid":41404,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8981fb726f919ac2a6aa8043157bebdc767ff05a","tid":625361,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T11:32:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因管理不善而在全球航空公司排名榜節節下跌的國泰航空</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，一班由香港飛澳洲布里斯班、編號CX157航班，下午12時45分起飛後，懷疑出現故障折返香港，並通知機場控制塔作出局部戒備，航班於下午4時許安全降落。國泰航空網頁顯示，受影響航班預計今晚11時20分再出發。<br />\n<br />\n機場管理局表示，下午3時54分接獲機場控制塔通知，一班香港飛往布里斯班的國泰航班CX157需要折返，航班於下午4時38分安全降落，機場運作不受影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180411/bkn-20180411184807307-0411_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180411%2Fbkn-20180411184807307-0411_00822_001.html&d=nuuFdWoD5eNPs7%2ByTS60fr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=2144718b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180411/bkn-20180411184807307-0411_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"35531760c20ba9bace6be0c2454cc37398010ef8","tid":625361,"uid":67065,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T11:54:01.000Z","msg":"無記錯直航先8個幾鐘<br />\n飛左4個鐘先回頭"},{"pid":"132d0b71fe3ebd93f6451fb37aa7850ef80e426e","tid":625361,"uid":60366,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T11:58:59.000Z","msg":"個title有問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由係HK起飛到係HK降落只係4粒鐘<br />\n<br />\n咁應該係起飛兩粒鐘到左右就開始折返啦"},{"pid":"79a2c513ffaa744c5d09d6f7a70fd60f929d4ea2","tid":625361,"uid":476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35531760c20ba9bace6be0c2454cc37398010ef8","tid":625361,"uid":67065,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T11:54:01.000Z","msg":"無記錯直航先8個幾鐘<br />\n飛左4個鐘先回頭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"